my man ( 私の男 watashi no otoko ) is a 2014 japanese romantic drama film directed by kazuyoshi kumakiri and based on kazuki sakuraba 's watashi no otoko novel .   it was released on 14 june 2014 in japan .   the film won the golden george at the 36th moscow international film festival and tadanobu asano won the award for best actor .   fumi nikaidō won international rising star award for this film at new york asian film festival and best actress at 6th tama film awards .